Class Summary 
Class Description
Asteroids
Asteroid Class which inherits from moons
Driver
Main Driver Class used to run the program
Moons
Moon Class which extends Planets
Planets
Planet Class which inherits all the methods, variables from the Sun Class
SolarObjects
SolarObjects class (SuperClass) All Objects (Planets,Moons,Asteroids,Sun) inherit this class
SolarSystem
This class provides a graphical user interface to a model of the solar system
Sun
Sun Class used to store all the information for a sun
Window
This class has been created to add all the objects on the screen Polymorphism is used to add Planets / Moon / Asteroids which is then added into a SolarObjects Array A while (true) loop is used to create the animation on the screen
